update

public void update(int dt)
the update method lets states perform their default transitions and also performs the carry over of time once a state is left

Parameters:
dt - the time that this state manager shall progress in milliseconds

proposeState

public boolean proposeState(GOState.StateType proposal)
this method allow to propose a state. the state is accepted if it has a higher priority (meaning higher index in the state table) than the current state

Parameters:
proposal - the proposed state
Returns:
true if the state was accepted, false if not.
